*     CURIND      indenting for this line
*     SPACE       temporary shift in indenting, this line only
*     TABSIZ      size of tabs (3 at present)
*     TABNOW      immediate tab shift (includes line issued on)
*     TABNXT      tab shift starting on the next line.
*     IF LEV      current level of block IF statements
